descr: "This is the base resource type for everything."

fields.name: id
fields.descr: "The logical id of the resource, as used in the URL for the resource. Once assigned, this value never changes."

fields.name: meta
fields.descr: "The metadata about the resource. This is content that is maintained by the infrastructure. Changes to the content may not always be associated with version changes to the resource."

fields.name: implicitRules
fields.descr: "A reference to a set of rules that were followed when the resource was constructed, and which must be understood when processing the content."

fields.name: language
fields.descr: "The base language in which the resource is written."
